  "1/f = 1/do + 1/di: 1/(-60) = 1/300 + 1/di. 1/di = -1/60 - 1/300 = -5/300 - 1/300 = -6/300 = -1/50. di = -50 cm. m = -(-50)/300 = +0.167 (virtual, upright, reduced).": "",
  "A projector uses a converging lens with f = 10 cm. A slide is placed 10.5 cm from the lens. How far away should the screen be placed?": "",
